Introduction
------------

This piece of software is the real time library for the satellite
emulation testbed OpenSAND used for bloc communications and events
management.

It was originally developped by CQ-Software ad the Open Network
Toolkit library called Margouilla.

License
-------

see COPYING.LGPL


Library
-------

The sources are in the src subdirectory. The sources build a library
that allow OpenSAND bloc communications and events management.
See the INSTALL file to learn how to build the libraries.
To compile an application using the OpenSAND margouilla library use the
following expression:
gcc `pkg-config opensand_margouilla --cflags` `pkg-config opensand_margouilla --libs` -o myappli myappli.c


